name: GEN 2 | SayCheese | Swift
bio: *hissing noises*! I'm GEN 2 | SayCheese | Swift. In high school, I was voted most likely to work at NASA. When my owner isn't watching, I steal their oversized sweaters and use them for litter paper. I'm not sorry. I can't wait to wake you up at 4am for seemingly no reason.
